                                                              APPLICATION
1.	Immersive training: Can be used by a person doing some outdoor games like skiing or jogging etc. Moreover, a person who is            riding bicycle for doing food deliveries, can see the google maps and the delivery details on his smart glasses.
2.	Seeing everything: Apart from the original view which is provided by the clear glasses, one can see the updates going on in his phone like texts, calls or any other notification. 
3.	Workplace Assistance: Any person who is at a certain job where his hands are fully loaded and cannot take out his phone, he can easily be updated to whatever is going on in his phone 
4.	Text-to-speech:- "Take a Note" to Evernote  exhibited a correction rate of 60 percent
